        "type": "automated_step",
        "label": "Shout",
        "description": "Triggered by the ingress channel's open descriptor (like demo 14's consumer — the In channel aliases the step's input place, so the open token both starts the job and carries the transport pointer). Drains aithericon.stream('feed') chunk by chunk and writes each chunk uppercased onto the 'shouted' data Out channel.",
